Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 Samekh复活的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后祭典的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是Samekh…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么巨大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类能拿它怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不来看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Samekh并不是坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是被我封印着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君回应了我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君已经不属于任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也不属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下只须解开皆水封印
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Samekh到了零时空间外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君就会成为这颗星球上的王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗星球是须方君的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你期盼已久的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗星球上最后的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想利用素体成为世界支配者的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多么无意义 明白了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来你也只是个恋爱中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这也是你可爱的地方 沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为我为什么长久以来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执着于这台素体Shinpathy（牙）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台Shinpathy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有驯化素体的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 Samekh只能由进藤须方驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我能连同进藤须方和Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 他会永远活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为我操纵的Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中的一个零件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把须方 还来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我的二刀流师出同门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做个了结吗 Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星剑 钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河十文字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Samekh已经是我的手足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与现在的我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等同于和Samekh战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还未见识Samekh真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些巫女已经察觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚苏醒的Samekh饥饿难忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渴求着复活所需的欲望能量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在发颤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事的是零时空间的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开零时空间封印的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Samekh为了成为原来的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吸干这颗星球的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 那样做的话这颗星球会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以Samekh的容量完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类灭亡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭人类 得到Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又能怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除皆水封印 进入第五阶段的Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能自由操纵时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为它的驾驭者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能成为时间旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以无数次重复美好的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后的未来会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要夺回一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙助先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被束缚着吗 时生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急动议！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海德的行为违反绮罗星规约第11条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即除籍处分！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是群极品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能迎来启程之日的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们只是我用来取得Samekh的垫脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么绮罗星 傻不傻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦人的小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,津名志家的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆水的素体？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然从神殿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 正中我下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏结束了 Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Samekh在我掌控中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你打坏了它们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所有素体都是Samekh的奴仆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Peshent（口）…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alephist（雄牛）…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是只属于我的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恒的梦即将开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你能撑到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Comment: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,津名志君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还…看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来我们只是被利用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类染指素体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始就是个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许对我们来说还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但素体是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们迟早会面对的可能性之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙妮？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过这次的这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海德错误地使用了素体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那台Samekh是台错误的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Daletos（门）在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的印记？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去的印记复苏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaddock（腕）…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tzadikt（纸莎草）…在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还留有一丝辉光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辉之鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 未能回归的素体们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘剑 纸吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗星十字团留下的乱摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我们收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿舍长？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挣脱Samekh的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发起行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢狱的看守者们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此巨大的王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么巨大的东西 怎么才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为靠一腔热血能克服所有的这份年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在压倒性的力量面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得见…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然自己跳进Samekh本体放出的王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一片青色的夜幕里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明自己的归宿和前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦碎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭典结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王之柱…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君…要封印Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让Samekh沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说须方君是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为封印Samekh才驾驶的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 地球得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗有它的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擅长表演被赋予的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有自信一直保护和子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就这么打算的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的儿子和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得见其他人看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底看见了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你我已经看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 须方还是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做的事和该做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零时空间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刹那 我也很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 拓人君这么做是理所当然的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能放任须方那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从遇见你那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是给我们欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那或许才是你的第一阶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我最近常想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是 没有遇见你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没来到岛上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠都说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羡慕那些一心只想着心仪男子的女性
